    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The technique of adding white or light media on a medium-toned or dark ground. The term is usually reserved for drawing, but painting and other image-making processes may also employ highlighting.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
